title: Trumpism Without Trump? Yellowjackets Theories! 1.19.22
itunes:title: Trumpism Without Trump? Yellowjackets Theories! 1.19.22
description:
In episode 1066, Jack and Miles are joined by comedian Ever Mainard to discuss Jack’s prayers kind of answered with new ITV doc…also Ghislaine ready to talk?, Thought experiment - Does Trumpism continue without Trump?, Anna’s Streaming Corner: Yellowjackets and more!

  1. Jack’s prayers kind of answered with new ITV doc…
  2. Also Ghislaine ready to talk?
  3. Thought experiment - Does Trumpism continue without Trump?
  4. Who Is King of Florida? Tensions Rise Between Trump and a Former Acolyte.


Listen: Autumn Antique by Teebs
